# Constants (Barrel)

- Exportar `assertTs`, `shouldTs`, `expectTs` de chai
- Exportar instâncias de Actions, Questions, Flows, Business
- Exportar base components quando usados globalmente
- Importar de paths `@/pages/`, `@/flows/`, `@/core-api/`
- Manter ordem: Asserções, Base Components, Actions, Questions, Flows, Business
